2T17:55:52.000Z","msg":"仲諗有冇意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n死左就係乜都冇"},{"pid":"4982517f6797214c58113822933a6d994a5492d4","tid":357261,"uid":106126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T20:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知自己會去邊<br />\n自己個意識會唔會消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會<br />\n感受過個感覺好得人驚"},{"pid":"39e8261f97a5b1f452cfabc886fb4dcb033285f2","tid":357261,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T21:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係人都會死<br />\n早死係福氣</blockquote><br />\n係 除非你想長生不死"},{"pid":"d0761eb519e1810abe3b74043e76a67111406e67","tid":357261,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:18:53.000Z","msg":"同樓豬一樣"},{"pid":"69873c76dec2415f06875f0c8762c17ca3a8ec67","tid":357261,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲諗有冇意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n死左就係乜都冇</blockquote><br />\n就係乜都冇先驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6376abc9ea97f80c3a3ca240135401cc7036fffd","tid":357261,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:24:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係人都會死<br />\n早死係福氣</blockquote><br />\n咁祝你早啲死"},{"pid":"92d5be43683625b446d25d3956a04be1265330cd","tid":357261,"uid":66997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:54:13.000Z","msg":"諗咗好耐點解自己未死都已經好可怕..."},{"pid":"6a4d4573c26e3e8d83f7c711374d832eb492dc3d","tid":357261,"uid":50123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T04:22:19.000Z","msg":"死唔可怕，可怕嘅只係時間線同過程<br />\n<br />\n當你自己知道差唔多嘅時候，你就唔會有恐懼"},{"pid":"6bd1bbb1cef75db8e1683691fd04366bd2c0be1f","tid":357261,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T04:23:52.000Z","msg":"唯一既恐懼就係<br />\n屌，仲要等咁耐？"},{"pid":"d2776ff3de503dd6a1fe71c561b6c461b0b2a79a","tid":357261,"uid":42081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T04:31:14.000Z","msg":"反而我係覺得 你點都唔會知死後嘅情形啦 所以唔洗多諗 用最簡單嘅方法咁諗 死後一係繼續有意識 一係冇架姐 因此冇必要諗咁多(反正你在生都唔會知答案)"},{"pid":"61066b807fa342678e0a4c2ec17b5084f0d42f19","tid":357261,"uid":42081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T04:33:46.000Z","msg":"老土D講句 未知生 焉知死 再黎多句更老土嘅 活在當下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eef02280412d88ff626828e59cc305e6052f9b6","tid":357261,"uid":35501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T04:37:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唯一既恐懼就係<br />\n屌，仲要等咁耐？</blockquote><br />\n我都想講<br />\n係就快啦屌<br />\n唔會自殺但好想死"},{"pid":"c03ed05847fb72b5eec6ebf5270f4eaf09a020a7","tid":357261,"uid":61363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T04:40:51.000Z","msg":"我都會，會諗埋宇宙同時間，究竟自己未出世前個意識係點，死之後打後嘅時間仲係點存在，而宇宙之外會唔會有嘢，定係宇宙已經係一切"},{"pid":"3599565ddd5c67fc3e7eb4f122b7b54aebb81a87","tid":357261,"uid":98927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T04:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知自己會去邊<br />\n自己個意識會唔會消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n久唔久就會咁，個人會驚到標哂冷汗，尤其見倒啲細路，諗起佢地九十歲住緊老人院嗰陣我喺邊就驚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特登要諗又唔會驚，係喺思路有條路行行下就墮咗入去出唔返嚟直至標哂冷汗先完<br />\n<br />\n有諗過睇心理醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8a35c6c94a067450616df0ac38fa355dcd0b6b","tid":357261,"uid":73644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲諗有冇意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n死左就係乜都冇</blockquote><br />\n就係乜都冇先驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乜都冇 咁邊度有得你驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8745d82cdc48d4988b60f7d2da3e1f0f7af48044","tid":357261,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6469c32873dc75da9b4b9f94c18d9425351473df","tid":357261,"uid":46197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T05:51:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係人都會死<br />\n早死係福氣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n捱30年按揭，人生已完"}]}